{"tid":1473153,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「重提/感人」我地5年前輸左 今次仲點可以輸","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T07:06:32.000Z","uid":36716,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec8bba60c1ff84cf9cc6a70291a2f2655e6dbfeb","tid":1473153,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2tYZbS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2tYZbS.jpg&h=3625358d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五年前,我們輸了,一敗涂地。我哋失去朋友，失去家人，失去部分的自我。如今我們有機會<br />\n扭轉乾坤，你哋知道自己的團隊和任務，討回自由，救他們回來！<br />\n<br />\n我想同年輕一輩講，對唔住。5年前因為我地輸左而令你地今個暑假咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n希望有朝一日，我哋可以除低口罩係立法會相認"},{"pid":"c4ffd1136316a678bce49b1c542e0278fee073f4","tid":1473153,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:29:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818， 追討黑警濫權!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818，正視警黑合作</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXPug1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXPug1n.jpg&h=448ec9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89de63474f9e7e5c00d424476deaea96e8a85dd8","tid":1473153,"uid":36716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"唔止係相認，而係除低口罩係立法會下慶祝"},{"pid":"cdaa8c52bdd3c6188887900ec8e2ac9bb006b845","tid":1473153,"uid":42246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:32:05.000Z","msg":"5年前輸既代價好重<br />\n冇左普選 dq 一地兩檢  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次再輸 我同你講一定玩完<br />\n辱警法 國歌法 口罩法 23條<br />\n<br />\n一定跟住來<br />\n<br />\n到時警犬係特權階層 姦你老婆都要忍"},{"pid":"97347b0e0a6f43816924b1691829355c78f121f9","tid":1473153,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdaa8c52bdd3c6188887900ec8e2ac9bb006b845","tid":1473153,"uid":42246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"ci